{#
/**
 * @file
 * A utility template for tables that don't need to extend another template.
 *
 * Horizontally scrollable tables extend the table-scrollable template. If a
 * table is not scrollable, there is no need to extend any template. However,
 * Twig only provides the ability to conditionally choose the template that
 * should be extended. It is not possible to conditionally extend or not-extend.
 *
 * This template is for tables that don't actually need to extend a template.
 * Extending this will have the same end result as not extending a template at
 * all.
 *
 * @see https://twig.symfony.com/doc/3.x/tags/extends.html#conditional-inheritance
 */
#}
{% block table %}
{% endblock %}
